Body: Nice topic, @cryptosolar, and awesome infographic!  Speaking about Ignis... For those that like free tokens and solving puzzles, Nxter.org has weekly faucets going on.  https://www.nxter.org/puzzles/  This week there's 100 free IGNIS to get: https://www.nxter.org/alice-lost-her-ignis-passphrase/  The solution is a passphrase to an account on the Ignis blockchain. Solve the puzzle, log in to the account first and transfer IGNIS out.
